</tr>
<tr>
<td><span>青岛“山东会客厅”</span></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table></p>
<p>
<table>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><span><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200820/1fa04308447b412bbb171d36e04eebf4.jpeg" /></span></td>
